title: S.E.C. Sues Elon Musk to Compel Him to Testify on Twitter Purchase
description: The agency said Mr. Musk was subpoenaed to testify last month about his purchases of Twitter’s stock last year, but he failed to appear.

title: Elon Musk Says SpaceX Could Land on Mars in 3 to 4 Years
description: The prediction is the latest in a series of ambitious timelines for reaching the red planet that the entrepreneur has previously failed to meet.
